Heto, kainin mo ito at gumising ka.

00:40:17.469 --> 00:40:19.439
Ang iyong turn. Dito.

00:40:20.309 --> 00:40:21.339
Salamat.

00:40:24.209 --> 00:40:25.209
Magaling akong sidekick diba?

